listings.ListingDescription: Wscape to a serene scandinavian-inspired cabin nestled in the mountain, only 15 minutes from Tremblant. Immerse yourself in the tranquility of nature while enjoying modern comfort, including a private spa and sauna.

listings.ListingTitle: Tremblant Architect Glass Treehouse Spa, Luxe/View
listings.ListingDescription: Unique & Secluded all white Glass Treehouse with Breathtaking Mont-Tremblant mountains views! All white design, the cabin is majestically glazed architectural space combining natural simplicity and contemporary luxury, 10 min from village of Mont-Tremblant, Ski Tremblant, Lacs & Beaches.
